Privacy Policy for Arch Survey App

Last Updated: September 28, 2023
Introduction
Welcome to Arch Survey, a mobile application (the "App") developed by Samarra Solutions. Arch Survey is designed to provide simple daily surveys to users, where they can earn points by answering questions and later convert those points into cash at the end of each month. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy is intended to inform you about how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use the App.
By downloading, installing, or using the App, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
Information We Collect
1. Personal Information: To personalize your experience and facilitate payments, we collect your name and phone number. We do not share this information with any third party, as we are committed to keeping your personal details confidential. Your name and phone number are solely used for internal purposes, including payment processing.
2. Survey Responses: We collect the survey responses you provide to earn points. These responses are used for the purpose of assigning points based on your participation. Your survey responses are not shared with any third party.
3. Usage Data: We may collect information about your interaction with the App, including the number of surveys completed, points earned, and general usage patterns. This data is used to improve the App's functionality and user experience.
4. Advertisements: The App serves advertisements during survey quizzes. Advertisers may collect certain non-personal information to display relevant ads. Please refer to the Advertisers' privacy policies for details on their data collection and usage practices.
How We Use Your Information
We use your personal information, survey responses, and usage data for the following purposes:
1. Personalization: Your name and phone number are used to personalize your experience within the App and to facilitate payments.
2. Payment Processing: Your name and phone number are used to process payments when you choose to convert your earned points into cash at the end of each month.
3. App Improvement: We analyze usage data to improve the functionality and content of the App, ensuring a better user experience.
Data Security
We take data security seriously and employ reasonable administrative, technical, and physical measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. Your personal information is stored securely and is only accessible to authorized personnel who require it for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy.
Third-Party Links
The App may contain links to third-party websites or services. Please be aware that we are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these third parties. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of these websites or services before providing any personal information.
Contact Us
If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
Email: samarrasolutions@gmail.com
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our data practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the App or by other means as required by applicable law.
Please review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.
By using the App after the effective date of any modifications to this Privacy Policy, you consent to the updated practices as described in the revised Privacy Policy.
Thank you for choosing Arch Survey. Your privacy is important to us, and we appreciate your trust in us.
